invention-title.$: Antibodies against CD38 for treatment of multiple myeloma
Antibodies against CD38 for treatment of multiple myeloma

p.$: Isolated human monoclonal antibodies which bind to human CD38, and related antibody-based compositions and molecules, are disclosed. Also disclosed are pharmaceutical compositions comprising the human antibodies, and therapeutic and diagnostic methods for using the human antibodies.
